3) North Star Metric

North Star Metric:
Accessorial Miss Rate — the percentage of shipments where the system failed to
recommend a required accessorial that the carrier later charged.

Why it matters:
Every 1% reduction in miss rate directly reduces post-delivery billing disputes
and customer complaints.

